OL,3,CVictim of abuser set for early release
OL,4,C'failed by system'
OL,6,FA woman whose abusive ex-husband was
OL,7,Fjailed after threatening to kill her
OL,8,Fand attacking another woman says it is
OL,9,Fa "kick in the teeth" that he will be
OL,10,Freleased early.
OL,12,FEx-army sergeant Martin Underwood, 49,
OL,13,Fattacked Elizabeth Hudson at their
OL,14,Fhome in Barnsley in April 2021.
OL,16,FWhile on bail, he assaulted another
OL,17,Fwoman.
OL,19,FHe was sentenced to six years and
OL,20,Fthree months in prison in February of
OL,21,Flast year.
