OL,3,CVictim of abuser set for early release
OL,4,C'failed by system'
OL,6,FBut Ms Hudson has received a letter
OL,7,Ffrom the Ministry of Justice outlining
OL,8,Fplans to release him early as part of
OL,9,Fefforts to reduce prison overcrowding.
OL,11,FShe said: "(It was) just like another
OL,12,Fkick in the teeth from a system that
OL,13,Fhasn't done enough to protect me all
OL,14,Falong.
OL,16,F"I was angry, sobbed, all the old
OL,17,Ffeelings are back, I've got PTSD
OL,18,Fsymptoms. They're rearing their ugly
OL,19,Fhead quite badly."
