OL,3,CVictim of abuser set for early release
OL,4,C'failed by system'
OL,6,FMs Hudson had been in what she called
OL,7,Fan "incredibly difficult" relationship
OL,8,Fwith Underwood for 15 years before the
OL,9,Ffinal attack, during which he hit her
OL,10,Fwith a phone, punched her in the
OL,11,Fstomach, held a knife to the face and
OL,12,Fthreatened to killer her and himself.
OL,14,FHe slashed her arm before she managed
OL,15,Fto escape.
OL,17,F"If I hadn't got out of that house I
OL,18,Fwouldn't be here today," she said.
