OL,3,CVictim of abuser set for early release
OL,4,C'failed by system'
OL,6,FUnderwood was arrested but given bail.
OL,7,FIn August 2022 he attacked a second
OL,8,Fwoman.
OL,10,FHe eventually admitted making threats
OL,11,Fto kill, assault occasioning actual
OL,12,Fbodily harm and non-fatal suffocation.
OL,14,FDuring his sentencing at Sheffield
OL,15,FCrown Court he was told by a judge he
OL,16,Fposed a "significant risk" to future
OL,17,Fpartners.
