OL,3,CVictim of abuser set for early release
OL,4,C'failed by system'
OL,6,FHowever, last Friday Ms Hudson was
OL,7,Ftold he would be released by June
OL,8,F2025, and could be freed as early as
OL,9,FDecember this year.
OL,11,FIt comes as the government tries to
OL,12,Fprevent the prison system collapsing
OL,13,Fby reducing the minimum an inmate must
OL,14,Fserve from 50% to 40% of their
OL,15,Fsentence.
OL,17,FMinisters had previously said domestic
OL,18,Fabusers would not be eligible for
OL,19,Fearly release.
