OL,3,CVictim of abuser set for early release
OL,4,C'failed by system'
OL,6,FMs Hudson said: "I'm very angry and
OL,7,Flet down by the system I don't have
OL,8,Fany faith in it. The Probation Service
OL,9,Fis clearly struggling... I know what a
OL,10,Fstate that's in and now they're
OL,11,Freleasing loads and loads of dangerous
OL,12,Fpeople when the service is already
OL,13,Fstruggling and crumbling.
OL,15,F"You couldn't have a more clear cut
OL,16,Fexample of abuse - serious domestic
OL,17,Fabuse than in my case - and yet he's
OL,18,Feligible. How many others are slipping
OL,19,Fthrough?
