OL,6,F"I don't think any victim of crime is
OL,7,Fparticularly safe at the minute."
OL,9,FLast week, the prison population in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales hit 88,521 - the
OL,11,Fhighest level ever recorded.
OL,13,FWithout changes, it was predicted
OL,14,Fthere would be almost 100,000
OL,15,Fprisoners by 2025.
OL,17,FThe official usable capacity is
OL,18,Fcurrently 88,895, but several new
OL,19,Fjails are being built and the Labour
OL,20,Fgovernment has promised to increase
OL,21,Fconstruction.
