OL,6,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood told
OL,7,Fbroadcasters the decision to release
OL,8,Fsome prisoners early was not one the
OL,9,Fgovernment "wanted to make, but it was
OL,10,Fthe only option left on the table
OL,11,Fbecause the alternative would have
OL,12,Fseen the total collapse of the
OL,13,Fcriminal justice system in this
OL,14,Fcountry".
